      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "8972-9037",
      "markText": "人群立刻跟着它蜂拥而下，他们从岩石上涌下去，跳到“野兽”身上，叫着、打着、咬着、撕着。没有话语、也没有动作，只有牙齿和爪子在撕扯。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8972&rangeEnd=9037",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8972&rangeEnd=9037"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_3_1600-1622",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1600-1622",
      "markText": "为了爱自己，才必须爱他人，或者装出来爱他人。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1600&rangeEnd=1622",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1600&rangeEnd=1622"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_5_16613-16637",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "16613-16637",
      "markText": "“他可不叫胖子，”拉尔夫喊道，“他名叫猪崽子！”",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16613&rangeEnd=16637",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16613&rangeEnd=16637"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_9_14825-14845",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "14825-14845",
      "markText": "“我是想说……大概野兽不过是咱们自己。”",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=14825&rangeEnd=14845",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=14825&rangeEnd=14845"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_13_9186-9223",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "9186-9223",
      "markText": "即使在大雨滂沱之中，他们也能看得出那“野兽”小得可怜，它的鲜血染红了沙滩。",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=9186&rangeEnd=9223",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=9186&rangeEnd=9223"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_4_3560-3630",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3560-3630",
      "markText": "一部成功的小说应当打乱读者的生活，让他/她误了约会、茶饭不思、忘记遛狗。而在一流的小说中，作者的想象成为了读者的现实。它会闪耀，炽热且猛烈。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3560&rangeEnd=3630",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3560&rangeEnd=3630"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_5_20039-20073",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "20039-20073",
      "markText": "“他刚找到海螺那阵子我就跟他在一起。我早就跟他在一块儿，比谁都早。”",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=20039&rangeEnd=20073",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=20039&rangeEnd=20073"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_8_5644-5666",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5644-5666",
      "markText": "杰克在面具后面躲着，摆脱了羞耻感和自我意识。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5644&rangeEnd=5666",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5644&rangeEnd=5666"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_5_20868-20955",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "20868-20955",
      "markText": "“叫你猪崽子总比叫胖子好，”拉尔夫最后说，带着一种真正领导派头的直率说道，“不管怎么样，要是你感到不高兴，我为此而抱歉。好了，回去吧，猪崽子，去点名。那是你的活儿。回头见。”",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=20868&rangeEnd=20955",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=20868&rangeEnd=20955"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_11_6664-6758",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6664-6758",
      "markText": "与此同时，罗伯特尖声地叫，狂蹦乱跳地拼命挣扎。杰克揪住了他的头发，挥舞着刀子。杰克背后是罗杰，正抢上前来。孩子们齐声叫喊的声音越来越响，就像他们在举行什么仪式，就像接近了跳舞和打猎的尾声。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6664&rangeEnd=6758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6664&rangeEnd=6758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_3_2922-2978",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2922-2978",
      "markText": "不禁想到核战争的另一面——亦即或许只有用核战争，才能消灭掉人类这只叮在腐肉上的苍蝇，让地球恢复到从前的自然状况。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2922&rangeEnd=2978",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2922&rangeEnd=2978"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_12_22280-22305",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "22280-22305",
      "markText": "“你是个傻小子，”蝇王说道，“一个无知的傻小子。”",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=22280&rangeEnd=22305",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=22280&rangeEnd=22305"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_14_17421-17466",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "17421-17466",
      "markText": "现在他真正是个头领了，他手持长矛东戳戳西刺刺。悬挂在他左手摇晃着的，是猪崽子破碎了的眼镜。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=17421&rangeEnd=17466",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=17421&rangeEnd=17466"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_16_20502-20545",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "20502-20545",
      "markText": "他失声痛哭：为童心的泯灭和人性的黑暗而悲泣，为忠实而有头脑的朋友猪崽子坠落惨死而悲泣。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=20502&rangeEnd=20545",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=20502&rangeEnd=20545"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_6_10914-10952",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10914-10952",
      "markText": "道亮闪闪的白光落到一块烂木头上。几乎同时升起了一缕轻烟，呛得拉尔夫干咳起来。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10914&rangeEnd=10952",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10914&rangeEnd=10952"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_14_3606-3620",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "3606-3620",
      "markText": "但是咱们跳过！咱们全都跳过！",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020416&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=3606&rangeEnd=3620",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f83321b0813ab6e79g016622?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=3606&rangeEnd=3620"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020416_5_27577-27621",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "27577-27621",
      "markText": "孩子们很清楚他为啥没下手：因为没有一刀刺进活物的那种狠劲；因为受不住喷涌而出的那股鲜血。",
